\frac{9x+8x^2+1}{x}
9+8x+1?
\begin{align} \frac{9x + 8x^2 +1}{x} & = \frac{9x}{x} + \frac{8x^2}{x} + \frac{1}{x} \\ & = 9 + 8x + \frac{1}{x} \\ & \neq 9 + 8x + 1 \\ \end{align}
x\times(9+8x+1)
 x(9+8x+1) = 9x+8x²+x\ne 9x+8x²+1 
1\cdot x^0
x
